# Reading 26: Intro to Identity
## MS Docs: Intro to Identity
- ASP.NET Core Identity is a Razor Class Library
- Can create a web app with authentication:
  - When creating a web application, select Change Authentication
  - Select Individual User Accouts, and click OK
- Can scaffold out a Razor project with authorization.
  - Includes log in form that displays when trying to access a restricted page, or when they have not been authenticated
